{"tid":101982,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港邊度有正宗日本沾麵食？","createTime":"2017-01-31T09:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T19:51:31.000Z","uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa65baea8f2e6d8349e1f71c6a9e3797f4592cb","tid":101982,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"頭先去左X吉拉麵叫左個沾麵<br />\n真係好垃圾<br />\n將個拉麵碌熟左再將個湯分開上就當沾麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個麵仲要係暖身而且濕淋淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個waitress仲要教我點食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常黎講，沾麵既麵條係乾身，麵質結實，麵條粗<br />\n而且係雪凍左，再沾落熱辣辣既濃湯汁度<br />\n我係新宿風雲兒食過<br />\n種味道香港食唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d17f62e9fa4d9b5a7e21d1e52c1f3e3d0125af","tid":101982,"uid":5538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:49:44.000Z","msg":"屯門 赤x拉麵"},{"pid":"fd5f95fd01de009acdc1e31a1997b19f63293dc9","tid":101982,"uid":837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:51:31.000Z","msg":"元朗 彩"}]}